{"tid":2104951,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"支冠肺炎｜盧寵茂指本港疫情如「山林大火」　深圳嘅人驚香港嘅人過去仲多","createTime":"2020-07-12T10:06:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-12T16:17:07.000Z","uid":224066,"like":5,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"d2218fed8708257ee4db541515f7719fc4da960e","tid":2104951,"uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T10:06:32.000Z","msg":"本港新支冠肺炎疫情惡化，更出現不少源頭不明的個案。港大深圳醫院院長盧寵茂今日（12日）出席港台節目《城市論壇》，以「山林大火」比喻本港疫情。他又指，內地疫情控制「非常出色」，又稱內地是成功例子，香港絕對應該學習，若要追回國家標準，香港每日應做近2萬個測試。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/4845686/org/99d5abb1ab52832e41f851ab0bd1ebe2.jpg/MNjRGYmK-cOu_DUVTor2kL-SW8GZ7ORgTPPLREzzy0Q?v=w1440\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F4845686%2Forg%2F99d5abb1ab52832e41f851ab0bd1ebe2.jpg%2FMNjRGYmK-cOu_DUVTor2kL-SW8GZ7ORgTPPLREzzy0Q%3Fv%3Dw1440&h=188ab6d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n指內地到港人士無新症<br />\n<br />\n港大深圳醫院院長盧寵茂以「山林大火」比喻本港疫情，認為政府早前控制好疫情後，並未有做好「下一步」，包括檢視社區內的隱形病人，而在關口上，亦未有控制好外來輸入個案。<br />\n<br />\n他批評，歐美地區出現大爆發，情況「一塌糊塗」，故口岸應做得更好，除非核酸測試到位，否則有關的高危地區，不能豁免強制檢疫的安排。相反，他稱由內地到港、且要隔離的人士中，基本上已無新症。<br />\n<br />\n「深圳嘅人驚香港嘅人過去仲多」<br />\n<br />\n港大深圳醫院的僱員及獲授權人員，現時屬於免檢疫人士之一。對於有指本港的豁免人士過多，盧寵茂說，應先區分高危區域，若由高危地方到港，同意需要嚴謹的檢疫措施。<br />\n<br />\n不過，<span class=\"red\">他稱醫院位於深圳，深圳至今只有462宗病例，而當地已經140日無本地個案，60日無輸入個案，看不到為何將深圳視為高風險地區，「如果你驚深圳嘅人過黎，不如調轉話，深圳嘅人驚香港嘅人過去仲多。」</span>他又指，所有同事到港前，都會先做核酸檢測。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><strong>每日應做近2萬個測試</strong></strong><br />\n<br />\n被問及每日的病毒檢測量達7,500個是否足夠，盧認為，現時疫情已在本地爆發，更涉及多區，故不應將7,500作「滿足上限」。他又以內地為例，當地每日做約378萬個核酸測試，若要追回國家標準，香港每日應做近2萬個測試。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/4831633/org/6a3d378a15a9a241cf82d2cb911507b2.jpg/fKFuq3ZahM-dNYp9Ox6Wv6FBMd7nWmK6Trl3b2S5d28?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F4831633%2Forg%2F6a3d378a15a9a241cf82d2cb911507b2.jpg%2FfKFuq3ZahM-dNYp9Ox6Wv6FBMd7nWmK6Trl3b2S5d28%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=ee1143a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong>內地疫情控制「非常出色」</strong><br />\n<br />\n盧又指，比起歐美地區，內地疫情控制「非常出色」，又稱內地是成功例子，香港絕對應該學習。他舉例指，北京早前曾爆發疫情，但在短時間已完全受控，過去四日已無新症。他說，內地做了大量核酸測試，北京在一周內，已做了接近900多萬個核酸測試，整個城市有超過2,000個採樣點，實驗費只需75元，費用全由政府負責，更動員全國之力，即使深圳亦派員到北京幫手。"},{"pid":"c2b0439c723f653ae8711b0cc78d37413ebc9e08","tid":2104951,"uid":97080,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T10:08:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"279ae7b822afab06946a1dddea898a8749e55f32","tid":2104951,"uid":55913,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T10:09:03.000Z","msg":"咁出色北韓同俄羅斯開左關未呀？"},{"pid":"d6b838d1176ecdbc77124f8676f7917973688482","tid":2104951,"uid":39871,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T10:09:37.000Z","msg":"風火山林<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n懷疑違反國安法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78210f88e84d6375c2149c24411ded509e237e83","tid":2104951,"uid":61280,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T10:11:04.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">都係侵侵至了解支支，&quot;唔驗咪冇咁多囉！！&quot;<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"2a9372de31c92d561622836e8773e9242791bd28","tid":2104951,"uid":6058,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T10:14:23.000Z","msg":"我睇錯做「風林火山」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5ab8988147e5f1664d10e95ca51c2b166406e08","tid":2104951,"uid":230104,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T10:17:03.000Z","msg":"盧寵茂指本港疫情如香港警察"},{"pid":"d378f5066da0d88d2834eeb4298b3616ecc760ab","tid":2104951,"uid":273703,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T10:19:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"940c178dee24659fd0fa5b802c7c46e525a34ee0","tid":2104951,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T10:19:38.000Z","msg":"腫教授喺深圳有固定小紅小娟"},{"pid":"708107d5e668f8b6410d3f646e8606bff0dc6ff0","tid":2104951,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T10:20:23.000Z","msg":"好想深圳嗰邊封我哋關<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6aada3953ecc7ba294834cbe2e241aa06210780","tid":2104951,"uid":28590,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T10:20:42.000Z","msg":"快d 開關啦咁 驚閪咩"},{"pid":"e2753186a85da6f73444849fdd2f0d6b052e3d2a","tid":2104951,"uid":34780,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T10:21:27.000Z","msg":"原來風林山火係咁玩<br />\n唔反了 唔反了"},{"pid":"2d1957d19e6fdfb38a37ba0de19b7b613c6b19e1","tid":2104951,"uid":41105,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T10:24:57.000Z","msg":"信政府，唔驚✌🏼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n美國都比你搞到幾百萬單case，中蟈會少過一千萬我地切柒啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a6f8db77e14800d8803630e5586540e5125fc96","tid":2104951,"uid":259088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T10:25:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ad145e4c8a1b4e584b1c1802e8f5ed3e970a7900","tid":2104951,"uid":53612,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T10:25:49.000Z","msg":"支持深圳封關"},{"pid":"1ac46bbb569c42ac327ede7a100e9a2780c79aad","tid":2104951,"uid":49609,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T10:26:47.000Z","msg":"咁完全封關啦"},{"pid":"bbf6d77e70f626db42c618864714ca51331c5467","tid":2104951,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T10:27:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f43f21ae5d81ff70c02495b2b3806cba1942c8c","tid":2104951,"uid":57532,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T10:28:28.000Z","msg":"睇到風林火山，以為講緊警暴問題嚴重。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f1f624d317ddcc3789836f8da5438e91825101c","tid":2104951,"uid":41389,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T10:36:23.000Z","msg":"咁佢返左去深圳未？"},{"pid":"4aab973046b537aa5df2d6219d10875217c3696e","tid":2104951,"uid":81399,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T10:38:03.000Z","msg":"幾時先過去武漢救災呀？<br />\n使唔使買埋機票俾盧生去呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5c83a44bb60bfe184549c8f1a1a8918de170a7f","tid":2104951,"uid":123738,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T11:55:44.000Z","msg":"支那仲唔封關？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"176812bb9267f2deab002e6c0652fb846833ae7a","tid":2104951,"uid":25424,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T12:16:34.000Z","msg":"香港好危險，所以唔好黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"107b46cb41da7d1ad9f6876f0903cf89c29f2108","tid":2104951,"uid":120678,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T14:10:48.000Z","msg":"盧寵茂好似係肝臟移植果邊，而家搞流行病學好似撈過界喎。"},{"pid":"06d388e68b0879b9adcb7df5d46d541d3ec4e85e","tid":2104951,"uid":85586,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T14:14:01.000Z","msg":"支持新移民全部返鄉下<br />\n鄉下最安全<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57717cb426dabe94c9f1aff8f183a3